{"tid":668935,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"3警截查疑人時涉「砌生豬肉」妨礙司法公正　押後至下月再預審","createTime":"2018-05-18T04:51:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T06:32:30.000Z","uid":184679,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"510d675e7cf3cf64b166c3c939f73fbc6c0f69e6","tid":668935,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T04:51:04.000Z","msg":"3名警員及警長涉在黃大仙截查一名可疑男子時意圖妨害司法公正，3人早前均否認一項作出傾向並意圖妨害司法公正罪，案件今日（18日）預審。辯方指閉路電視影到的人並非本案3名被告，以及爭議被告的行為不屬意圖妨害司法公正。另控方指出在傳召的9名證人中，有3人的證供謄本仍未完成整理，故裁判官押後至6月4日作第2次預審，期間3名被告續准以500元現金保釋。<br />\n<br />\n3名被告為男警員鄧文祖（34歲）、女警員李軒賴（31歲）及男警長伍肇龍（44歲），辯方透露次被告現時懷孕，預產期為本月10月，要求本案可於7月中旬開審。控罪指各被告於前年12月20日至去年1月22日意圖妨害司法公正，即在有關蕭志邦於前年12月20日在黃大仙下邨被捕一案，他們所作的證人口供或警察記事冊口供中作虛假陳述，3人早前已被停職。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2075899/%E6%88%AA%E6%9F%A5%E7%96%91%E4%BA%BA%E6%99%82%E6%B6%89%E5%A6%A8%E7%A4%99%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E5%85%AC%E6%AD%A3%E3%80%803%E8%AD%A6%E6%8A%BC%E5%BE%8C%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%8B%E6%9C%88%E5%86%8D%E9%A0%90%E5%AF%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2075899%2F%25E6%2588%25AA%25E6%259F%25A5%25E7%2596%2591%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%25A6%25A8%25E7%25A4%2599%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E3%2580%25803%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258A%25BC%25E5%25BE%258C%25E8%2587%25B3%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2586%258D%25E9%25A0%2590%25E5%25AF%25A9&d=YZq9Yv%2FB7MY8GC9yKNV6S7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=7930f6da\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2075899/%E6%88%AA%E6%9F%A5%E7%96%91%E4%BA%BA%E6%99%82%E6%B6%89%E5%A6%A8%E7%A4%99%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E5%85%AC%E6%AD%A3%E3%80%803%E8%AD%A6%E6%8A%BC%E5%BE%8C%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%8B%E6%9C%88%E5%86%8D%E9%A0%90%E5%AF%A9</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc86cc3895f559a6a1efe08a2236c1b624114c27","tid":668935,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T04:53:00.000Z","msg":"東九龍總區衝鋒隊3名警員，在黃大仙截查一名男子時涉嫌「砌生豬肉」，指該男子疑藏有冰毒及管有吸毒工具，拘捕了該男子並帶返警署錄取口供。惟該男子事後與家人稱指該些工具非在他身上找到，再向警方投訴。經調查後，三警被控一項妨礙司法公正罪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/167708/3%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%99%82%E6%B6%89-%E7%A0%8C%E7%94%9F%E8%B1%AC%E8%82%89-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E5%A6%A8%E7%A4%99%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E5%85%AC%E6%AD%A3%E7%BD%AA%E6%8F%90%E5%A0%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F167708%2F3%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%25B6%2589-%25E7%25A0%258C%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25B1%25AC%25E8%2582%2589-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%25A6%25A8%25E7%25A4%2599%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%25A0%2582&d=YZq9Yv%2FB7MY8GC9yKNV6S7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=10008856\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/167708/3%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%99%82%E6%B6%89-%E7%A0%8C%E7%94%9F%E8%B1%AC%E8%82%89-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E5%A6%A8%E7%A4%99%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E5%85%AC%E6%AD%A3%E7%BD%AA%E6%8F%90%E5%A0%82</a>"},{"pid":"79346e8bb2063f9c553c91a44f2a78d9ca02a260","tid":668935,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T04:55:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a84347266567988a2c2985ac68ca401a631af749","tid":668935,"uid":163758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T05:03:52.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n警犬死全家"},{"pid":"2cd27f4ffd1ace0eed146c53d8a8c20095b3578f","tid":668935,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T05:27:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmo